題名: 臺灣連鎖冷飲店消費者行為之探討—以清心冷飲站、五十嵐綠茶專賣店爲例The Study on the Exploration of Consumer Behavior for the Taiwan´s Tea Chain Store Brand — The Cases of Chin-Shin And 50Lan Tea Shop
作者: 吳隆中Long-jhong Wu
貢獻者: 李文魁 指導教授李樑堅 指導教授管理學院
關鍵詞: 茶飲店連鎖加盟創業EnteprenarshipChain-store franchiseTea-shops
日期: 2009
上傳時間: 2010-03-26 09:55:27  (UTC+8)
出版者: 碩士(Master)管理學院碩士班(Master of Postgraduate Programs in Management )
摘要: 近年來連鎖加盟系統在台灣快速的發展，加盟似乎已經成為想要創業者成全夢想的最佳捷徑，因為一般人都想藉由連鎖品牌的品牌力與成熟的經營策略，來幫助創業者順利創業成功，但並非所有創業者都能在創業的過程中成功創業，而連鎖品牌雖有成功的創業經驗，但在複製KNOW-HOW時是否成功掌握關鍵因素，也成為該品牌得以永續經營與長期獲利的立基點。本研究經現場實地進行問捲發放，研究範圍為清心力行店、學堂店、新田店及五十嵐文濱店、裕誠店、自由店等六家在高雄縣市兩大茶飲連鎖品牌的加盟店，利用隨機抽樣法由各家抽出三間門市，再針對問捲發放日期、時段分別進行隨機抽樣，一共收集400份有效問捲，並採用SPSS12.0版進行資料分析，並且採用描述性統計、Pearson積差相關、T檢定、單因子變異數分析、Scheffe事後比較與信度分析等方法。所收集之資料經統計驗證得知，本研究之五項假設，皆獲得部份成立。主要結論有四：（1）高雄縣市茶飲店消費者以女性、未婚、高中職程度、21～40歲之工商服務與學生族群居多，收入約四萬元以下。(2)下午二點後為消費顛峰時期，以休閒動機之舊客源為主，而地點與口耳相傳為重要管道。(3)中高收入女性與崇尚休閒嗜好、喜好藉茶類緩和情緒幫助思考與提神型態者，較重視茶類的品質。(4)不同生活型態消費者在評估茶類連鎖店時，最重視茶飲店形象、服務品質與店內環境等因素。The Chain store franchising system is fast growing in Taiwan, It helps those people who want to run business and the shortcut of the dream. Because people all think the brand will strength the chain brand and ripe management tactics can help the entrepreneur to start an undertaking smoothly successfully. Although chain brand has successful experience, not all entrepreneurs can succeed in starting the process of starting an undertaking. The key factor while duplicating KNOW-HOW, the ones know this brand can make profit for a long time continuously forever for this basic point.This study use the questionnaires, by giving the survey question to the customer about the Chin-shin Li-shin tea shop, Shan-Ton shop, Shin-ten shop and the 50 haze Wen-bin green tea shop, yu-chen green tea shop green tea shop and chin-yo green tea shop for totally six chain-store shops which in Kaohsiung city and county. BY random selection for one shop on each brand for different date and time; there are totally 400 effective questionnaires are collected altogether. Adopt SPSS12.0 edition to carry on analysis, including description statistics, Pearson relevant to accumulate difference, T inspection, single factor variance analysis, Scheffe comparison w afterwards to make a variation.From the verification of the data collected, five assumptions of this research are all established partly proved. There are four main conclusions: ( 1) The consumers of counties and cities in Kaohsjung serve with student's ethnicity in the majoritily with women, unmarried, the duty degree of high school, industry and commerce 21- 4 years old, gain under about 40,000 yuan. (2)In order to consume summit period after two o'clock in the afternoon, old traveler of the recreation motive as the core, and the place and an ear-spread are the important channel according to legend. (3)High income woman with fallow hobby, taste and those people who worship tea relaxation mood supernatural attitude person pay attention to the quality of the tea. (4)Different living type attitude consumers pay attention to image, service quality and such factors as the environment, etc.
相關連結: http://webpac.isu.edu.tw/webpac/detail/258806/http://handle.ncl.edu.tw/11296/ndltd/74905284476243836409
